official_title: A bill to provide that the unincorporated territory of Guam shall be represented in Congress by a Territorial Deputy to the House or Representatives.

summary.text: Provides that the unincorporated territory of Guam shall be represented in Congress by a Territorial Deputy to the House of Representatives. Sets forth the requirements for candidates for such office and the procedure for conducting the election thereof.
